<br>
Those random research pages/words sell for 2-4pp each in KC.  They drop fairly commonly, are stackable, and don't weigh much.  And two or three bags should be enough to collect them all.  And gems do drop in KC.  I usually get 1 maybe 2 a night, and they sell for 50-80pp a piece.<br>
<br>
I have a cleric I play in KC.  If I used Naltron's on everyone in the group, I would probably loose money.  But as it is, I usually only natlron's the enchanter, MT, and sometimes the puller.  Everyone else gets pinzarn or nada.  But with symbol costs factored in, I still manage to net about 100-200pp a night if not more.<br>
