The game is meant to be balanced. Everyone has their role. Yes clerics do have to spend money to keep their group alive, but they have benefits and perks, you'll rarely see an out of work cleric, where as its a lot, and i mean a LOT harder to find a group as an SK, or Ranger, Warr at times too. Because here are so many tanks out there, we cant find groups as often. And usually the tanks with better equip (not always) are wanted prefferably because  they can keep aggro better etc...<br>
<br>
